                acts as Eliexpress's API.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-6 opacity-80 ">ReactJS - ExpressJS - MongoDB</p>
            </div>
            <div class="projectImage  top-0 absolute left-0 hidden xl:block  ">
              <img
                src={Astro.resolve("../assets/dash1.png")}
