              <p class="leading-8 mb-6 bg-tertiary p-4 rounded opacity-95">
                A cli tool that scaffolds a NextJs-Typescript-TailwindCSS
                project in seconds.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-6 opacity-80 ">Typescript</p>
              <a
                href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/dax-stax"
                rel="noreferrer"
                target="_blank"
                aria-label="Dax Stax CLI link"
                ><i
                  class="fa fa-external-link text-secondary text-lg"
                  aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="projectImage  top-0 absolute right-0 hidden xl:block ">
